<title>USA: CFM Tech gets $16.1 mln order.</title>
<headline>CFM Tech gets $16.1 mln order.</headline>
<dateline>WEST CHESTER, Pa. 1996-12-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>CFM Technologies Inc said on Friday that it has received a $16.1 million order from LG International Co Ltd's American unit.</p>
<p>The order is for six Full Flow FPD tools, whcih will be used for precision cleaning and etching of flat panel displays.</p>
<p>CFM said that installation is planned for the second and third quarters of calendar 1997.</p>
<p>CFM, a manufacturer of advanced cleaning equipment for the semiconductor and flat panel display industries, had total revenues of $44 million in 1995.</p>
